        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 6 c-e:\nImmunogold localization of synaptopdin to the spine apparatus of synapses in the in stratum radiatum of the hippocampal CA3 region\nFigs. 5-9. Localization of the immunoperoxidase reaction product at spine apparatuses of various hippocampal synapses.. Experimental description: Twelve adult male Sprague-Dawley rats (250-350 g; Charles River, Sulzfeld, Germany) housed under standard laboratory conditions were used in this study." ;
